<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Booking Modified</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
        }
        .changes {
            background-color: #e2e3e5;
            border: 1px solid #d6d8db;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .original {
            text-decoration: line-through;
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        .updated {
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Booking Modified</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        
        <p>Your booking has been modified. Here are the updated details:</p>
        
        <div class="changes">
            <h3>Modified Details</h3>
            {{#if timeChanged}}
            <p>
                <strong>Time:</strong><br>
                <span class="original">{{originalTime}}</span><br>
                <span class="updated">{{newTime}}</span>
            </p>
            {{/if}}
            {{#if durationChanged}}
            <p>
                <strong>Duration:</strong><br>
                <span class="original">{{originalDuration}} minutes</span><br>
                <span class="updated">{{newDuration}} minutes</span>
            </p>
            {{/if}}
            {{#if notesChanged}}
            <p>
                <strong>Notes:</strong><br>
                <span class="updated">{{notes}}</span>
            </p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <p>If you did not request these changes or have any questions, please contact us immediately.</p>
        
        <p>We look forward to seeing you!</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Eventide. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
